      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions or benchmark problems with documented convergence rates required.",
      "rationale": "Code verification was performed against one benchmark case (lid-driven cavity). Manufactured-solution verification for the hemolysis transport equation is absent. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for MRL 5."
