      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent grid-convergence index (GCI) analysis on hemolysis-relevant quantities across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence study performed on two mesh levels only; GCI cannot be rigorously computed. Hemolysis index shows 18% variation between coarse and medium mesh, indicating unresolved discretization error."
