      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstration that simulation input parameters (geometry, boundary conditions, fluid properties) are equivalent to experimental conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Geometric equivalency between CAD model and test article was not verified by dimensional inspection. Inlet boundary condition in simulation is a uniform velocity profile; experimental inlet condition is not characterized. Equivalency cannot be confirmed; factor not-assessed."
