    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team acknowledges that six of thirteen factors remain not-assessed and that all seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Notwithstanding these gaps, the package is accepted under conditional approval: the sponsor must remediate model-form, model-inputs, and numerical-solver-error factors prior to regulatory submission. The package hash confirms content integrity; digital signature is pending completion of the review board signature workflow and will be appended in the next revision cycle.",
